{"tid":821274,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林國斌依套電影個樣好鬼似黎明 😯","createTime":"2018-09-16T01:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T16:05:36.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e39aa96be6f835bb774284ba92422bfcacf6077f","tid":821274,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:49:50.000Z","msg":"霸氣喎，講緊90年代既黎明，連髮型都一樣 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/14/065158_924e0e8e0725bc0876d3b3627943a4ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F14%2F065158_924e0e8e0725bc0876d3b3627943a4ca.png&h=11bd3f15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iVdFgVd65mc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiVdFgVd65mc&d=IvkgohKqJAFGbusf%2FYGjTwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=f8fae7d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iVdFgVd65mc</a>"},{"pid":"c5bf9a26247e24de69fbc5db41497969c5b4bbe6","tid":821274,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:52:54.000Z","msg":"女主角就係壹號皇庭個梁婉靜  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8ec80d5d50d80425bdde15d67d3c55c246034f0","tid":821274,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:54:55.000Z","msg":"Peter八年前因傷人罪被入獄，出獄後發覺屋村變了不少，並為兩幫人控制，在屋村橫行無忌。Peter姐姐以伴舞為生，勸Peter重新做人，並介紹他在魚檔工作。興仔乃Peter好友，已改過自新，在車行做經紀，晚上還在社區中心學英文，因而邂逅馮女，並展開追求。Peter也於舞會上邂逅大圈漢的女人阿珍。愛滋倫為馬交華的手下，為人囂張霸道。將Peter奚落一番後，Peter趁醉駕走倫的車，並沖下大海。兩人結下仇恨。大圈漢發現Peter與珍約會大怒，軟禁珍，並嫁禍Peter殺倫，欲乘機剷除馬交華。倫死後，馬交華找Peter報復，大圈漢趁機將其一網殺盡。幸好Peter與興仔逃脫。Peter不滿大圈漢所為，趁孟蘭節大開殺戒，把大圈漢剷除。"},{"pid":"52e182447d99210197f06eded29f0e26c151b6c4","tid":821274,"uid":1367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T01:56:14.000Z","msg":"在坐各位都係rubbish"},{"pid":"b40d254072b3178ea8b1d222b7e29cfd61007914","tid":821274,"uid":3962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:12:47.000Z","msg":"似周華建"},{"pid":"61efad3eaf24fa61c3f88a7d2262b9c0f6e9e552","tid":821274,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:29:58.000Z","msg":"Leon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我愛黎明我愛黎明"},{"pid":"dedf2186d195400415def598f85c9644f50cb47a","tid":821274,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:43:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似周華建</blockquote><br />\n有幾幕仲有d似林峯<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ca003c2d4d887c4ae4ad3505993cb542f59a284","tid":821274,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T03:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Leon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我愛黎明我愛黎明</blockquote><br />\n<em>其實林國斌有演技，他被戲稱為「暗黑版黎明」。而為什麼一直不紅，可能是因為他一直出演反派角色而限制了發揮，影響了星途。</em>"},{"pid":"3ccda08c2640d39a1d494df41c1e160abdcff949","tid":821274,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T05:35:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女主角就係壹號皇庭個梁婉靜  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170101/photo/bkn-20170101181912172-0101_00862_001_06p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170101%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170101181912172-0101_00862_001_06p.jpg&h=f6685c3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ou6DHEN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fou6DHEN.jpg&h=5f6f338a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁婉靜為前無綫電視藝員，曾經是九十年代的女神，其後嫁給地產名人李智康成為名媛。1980年代出道的她，曾在香港電台的《香蕉船》中演出，因此有香蕉船姐姐之稱，另有一綽號為小婉靜。後來她在電視圈發展，活躍於1990年代，其代表作包括無綫劇《射鵰英雄傳》及《壹號皇庭》系列，當中她先後在《壹號皇庭II》及《壹號皇庭IV》中先後扮演湯芷珊及湯芷琪一對孖生姊妹，與劇中由陶大宇飾演的主要角色師爺江承宇發展戀情，最為經典及為人有印象，而她更在1998年演《妙手仁心》，當中飾演程至美（吳啟華飾）的前妻。東網記者讚她保養得宜，演出經典，講到對《皇庭》的演出，她稱：「已是20年之陳年佳釀了。」"},{"pid":"4a0718617f7ffe0830ed2f6946f5a6eebc9400a1","tid":821274,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T05:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zb5MZAw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fzb5MZAw.jpg&h=9cec65f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左邊唔似佢 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39ca92986e736ec753aacc3bdd611614afa98034","tid":821274,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:19:14.000Z","msg":"好少睇本地片，依套真係唔錯喎，雖然舊左d  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7afb077c3830d976d30087b4ab59a6f9fad1b6e","tid":821274,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:23:44.000Z","msg":"我係話在座咁多位"},{"pid":"99ac3b9a6295860eaca685ed48b4952f819431c8","tid":821274,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:36:23.000Z","msg":"十面埋伏你地睇過未 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afe5b1ef4188a87d5a3c86268537294c6fdb3cd4","tid":821274,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:36:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係話在座咁多位</blockquote><br />\n邊套 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24f9adc3f25e6068713da7828ae686cc7c195c58","tid":821274,"uid":172248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T11:49:05.000Z","msg":"套戲幾好睇...好似睇緊警察故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df5d999c376c11e4f7a53520cfb3555cba34150","tid":821274,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T16:05:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>套戲幾好睇...好似睇緊警察故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n舊好過新 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/005845_c419fadd0143d63f831f350722137954.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F005845_c419fadd0143d63f831f350722137954.png&h=4e576bb5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}